204
00:18:16,130 --> 00:18:19,440
But Sunbae, I can't give up yet.

205
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:23,730
Eun Cho Rong, please respect someone else's feelings.

206
00:18:23,730 --> 00:18:27,880
Until now, I considered it a bit,

207
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,870
but not anymore.

208
00:18:29,870 --> 00:18:34,490
