219
00:19:26,210 --> 00:19:27,960
What do you think she wants to say?

220
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:30,290
Not sure. I don't know.

221
00:19:33,030 --> 00:19:37,630
They say there's some improvement.

222
00:19:37,630 --> 00:19:39,870
Unbelievable.

223
00:19:39,870 --> 00:19:41,800
That's unbelievable. 
    

224
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:46,090
