255
00:21:41,020 --> 00:21:44,240
Mountains, boats...

256
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:47,670
You two are so cringe. Stop holding hands.

257
00:21:47,670 --> 00:21:51,640
No way. I haven't held this hand in forever.

258
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:54,170
Aigoo, so nice and warm.

259
00:21:56,220 --> 00:22:00,190
