260
00:22:00,190 --> 00:22:01,580
Even I don't know.

261
00:22:01,580 --> 00:22:06,930
I don't know at what point it happened, either. It's a real mystery.

262
00:22:07,790 --> 00:22:10,580
- Honey, want more rice? 
 - Yes.

263
00:22:10,580 --> 00:22:13,300
