00:22:26,210 --> 00:22:30,420
Do Hyeong, ever since Unnie Mi Ja got cancer,

269
00:22:30,420 --> 00:22:33,050
he's lost his mind.

270
00:22:33,050 --> 00:22:36,580
- Completely. 
 - No.

271
00:22:36,580 --> 00:22:40,700
I think it happened after he didn't get the 9 o'clock anchor job.

272
00:22:40,700 --> 00:22:46,470
No. I think it happened after Eun Ho disappeared.

273
00:22:46,470 --> 00:22:48,150
Stop it.

274
00:22:50,380 --> 00:22:53,290
Give it to me. Hyung, I'll do it.

275
00:22:53,290 --> 00:22:55,110
You can't do that?

276
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:56,650
What are you doing?

277
00:22:57,230 --> 00:22:59,330
Give it to me. I'll do it.

278
00:22:59,330 --> 00:23:04,610
I heard some people can open a bottle with paper.

279
00:23:05,390 --> 00:23:07,300
I think I can do that.

280
00:23:07,300 --> 00:23:09,730
Sunbae, I think the bottle opener is the problem.

281
00:23:09,730 --> 00:23:12,430
No, no. That's...

282
00:23:12,430 --> 00:23:14,600
Is it that difficult?

283
00:23:14,600 --> 00:23:16,150
Aigoo.

284
00:23:19,280 --> 00:23:20,920
Come in.

285
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,800
Ju Yeon!

286
00:23:27,560 --> 00:23:29,720
- Department Head. 
 - Yes.

287
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:32,530
I have a question.

288
00:23:32,530 --> 00:23:34,780
Go ahead and ask!

289
00:23:35,290 --> 00:23:42,220
What does it mean if an announcer is taken off all programs at once?

290
00:23:42,890 --> 00:23:46,170
- That's... 
 - I know the answer.

291
00:23:46,170 --> 00:23:48,780
That means she quit.

292
00:23:48,780 --> 00:23:50,440
Aigoo, Hye Yeon.

293
00:23:50,440 --> 00:23:52,700
What? It's true.

294
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:55,100
Am I wrong?

295
00:23:55,100 --> 00:23:57,600
I think you're right, Hye Yeon.

296
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:59,690
Why do you ask, Ju Yeon?

297
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:02,000
But Department Head,

298
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:06,700
if they quit, their job wouldn't show up on their profile.

299
00:24:07,330 --> 00:24:09,700
Is that so?

300
00:24:09,700 --> 00:24:12,850
I know this one too. That means she's taking a sabbatical.

301
00:24:12,850 --> 00:24:15,410
Hye Yeon, we don't have sabbaticals here.

302
00:24:15,410 --> 00:24:18,050
No, but PPS does.

303
00:24:18,050 --> 00:24:20,760
It's very appealing to me.

304
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:23,950
Sunbae, that means she's taking a leave,

305
00:24:23,950 --> 00:24:26,510
a very long one.

306
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:29,090
But why? Do you need a break, too?

307
00:24:29,090 --> 00:24:31,620
If so, can you let me know? I want a break, too.

308
00:24:31,620 --> 00:24:34,730
No. I don't want a break.

309
00:24:38,230 --> 00:24:40,090
- Thank you, Department Head. 
 - Sure.

310
00:24:40,090 --> 00:24:42,200
What? Why are you thanking him?

311
00:24:42,200 --> 00:24:45,250
I answered everything. You should thank me.

312
00:24:47,250 --> 00:24:49,490
So in that spirit, let's...

313
00:24:49,490 --> 00:24:52,670
- By the way, Department Head. 
 - Yes, what else?

314
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:57,680
Do you know Announcer Jung Hyun Oh from PPS?

315
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:59,880
"Jung Hyun Oh"?

316
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:59,710
   

317
00:25:59,710 --> 00:26:02,780
   

318
00:26:34,140 --> 00:26:38,590
   

319
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:46,150
Hello.

320
00:26:46,150 --> 00:26:48,280
I heard you came to see me.

321
00:26:49,810 --> 00:26:53,950
Hello. I'm Kang Ju Yeon from Media N Seoul.

322
00:26:53,950 --> 00:26:57,900
I'm Jung Hyun Oh. I think we've met once before.

323
00:27:00,780 --> 00:27:02,240
 Yes. 

324
00:27:07,700 --> 00:27:10,560
 What brings you here? 

325
00:27:12,180 --> 00:27:15,440
I'm here because I have some questions.

326
00:27:16,970 --> 00:27:19,110
Sure, go ahead.

327
00:27:26,250 --> 00:27:28,470
Announcer Ju Eun Ho...

328
00:27:29,100 --> 00:27:31,590
where is she right now?

329
00:27:36,150 --> 00:27:38,750
I'd like to know first

330
00:27:39,550 --> 00:27:42,410
what your relationship is with Announcer Ju Eun Ho

331
00:27:42,410 --> 00:27:47,950
that you're asking me such a question.

332
00:27:50,250 --> 00:27:52,920
Then can I ask you, too?

333
00:27:53,860 --> 00:27:57,400
Sunbaenim, what is your relationship to Announcer Ju Eun Ho?

334
00:27:58,960 --> 00:28:00,890
We're colleagues.

335
00:28:04,570 --> 00:28:06,390
Seriously...

336
00:28:07,910 --> 00:28:10,520
Why are you saying, "Seriously"?

337
00:28:13,460 --> 00:28:17,020
Because I've seen you and Announcer Ju Eun Ho

338
00:28:17,020 --> 00:28:19,930
be affectionate with each other.

339
00:28:22,630 --> 00:28:25,600
Who are you to ask me such questions?

340
00:28:25,600 --> 00:28:28,740
As I've said before, I'm from Media N Seoul—

341
00:28:28,740 --> 00:28:30,020
No.

342
00:28:30,020 --> 00:28:33,630
I'm asking who you are to Ju Eun Ho.

343
00:28:36,660 --> 00:28:39,940
Announcer Ju Eun Ho's other personality,

344
00:28:40,820 --> 00:28:43,700
Ju Hye Ri, and I are in a relationship.

345
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:54,420
Her other personality? What are you talking about?

346
00:28:54,420 --> 00:28:59,040
Ju Eun Ho said she has Dissociative Identity Disorder.

347
00:29:08,560 --> 00:29:11,420
I found out only recently.

348
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:19,700
- Then how did you— 
 - Ju Eun Ho told me herself.

349
00:29:19,700 --> 00:29:22,050
She told you directly?

350
00:29:25,770 --> 00:29:28,110
Then you and Eun Ho...

351
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:29,950
What did you say? "A relationship"?

352
00:29:29,950 --> 00:29:36,040
I'm in a relationship with Ju Hye Ri, Announcer Ju Eun Ho's other personality.

353
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:40,590
So...

354
00:29:41,120 --> 00:29:46,100
Eun Ho has multiple personalities, and her other personality is Ju Hye Ri.

355
00:29:46,910 --> 00:29:48,800
But Ju Hye Ri...

356
00:29:48,800 --> 00:29:51,980
- Isn't that her younger sister's name? 
 - Yes.

357
00:29:52,560 --> 00:29:55,800
That's what Ju Eun Ho said, too,

358
00:29:55,800 --> 00:29:58,590
that her other personality is her younger sister.

359
00:29:59,750 --> 00:30:02,030
Oh, so...

360
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:05,530
You were dating Eun Ho's sister?

361
00:30:05,530 --> 00:30:10,330
Yes. I'm dating her younger sister.

362
00:30:10,970 --> 00:30:13,200
But you're saying that younger sister...

363
00:30:13,910 --> 00:30:15,860
is Eun Ho.

364
00:30:15,860 --> 00:30:18,410
Then you're saying you were dating Eun Ho. Am I wrong?

365
00:30:18,410 --> 00:30:20,440
That's true, but...

366
00:30:21,230 --> 00:30:24,560
the person I met was 28 years old

367
00:30:24,560 --> 00:30:27,260
and worked in a parking lot.

368
00:30:27,260 --> 00:30:29,400
Her name is Hye Ri.

369
00:30:31,090 --> 00:30:36,160
Sunbaenim, did you not know about this at all?

370
00:30:37,930 --> 00:30:40,430
 I-I'm really not Ju Eun Ho... 

371
00:30:40,430 --> 00:30:43,170
 What are you saying, Ju Eun Ho? Stop it! 

372
00:30:43,170 --> 00:30:45,510
 I'm not Ju Eun Ho! 

373
00:30:45,510 --> 00:30:47,440
 Hey, Ju Eun Ho! 

374
00:30:54,700 --> 00:30:57,740
 We had feelings for each other. 

375
00:31:04,370 --> 00:31:06,000
 Fine. 

376
00:31:07,070 --> 00:31:10,760
Even if she has multiple personalities, it's still Eun Ho.

377
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:13,960
The fact that Eun Ho had feelings for someone else...

378
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:16,240
What's odd about that?

379
00:31:16,920 --> 00:31:18,850
Because...

380
00:31:19,940 --> 00:31:21,530
that...

381
00:31:22,440 --> 00:31:25,630
- Because Eun Ho— 
 - She likes you, Sunbaenim?

382
00:31:30,380 --> 00:31:32,760
I have feelings for her.

383
00:31:34,560 --> 00:31:36,420
Do you mean...

384
00:31:36,420 --> 00:31:39,580
you like Eun Ho or Ju Hye Ri?

385
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:41,880
To be precise,

386
00:31:42,530 --> 00:31:44,930
I like Ju Hye Ri, who is inside Ju Eun Ho.

387
00:31:44,930 --> 00:31:46,350
Ultimately, that's Eun Ho.

388
00:31:46,350 --> 00:31:49,220
I wish that were the case, too, Sunbaenim.

389
00:31:50,930 --> 00:31:55,220
I wish the person I had met was Eun Ho.

390
00:31:55,220 --> 00:31:56,990
Because…

391
00:31:57,700 --> 00:31:59,740
no matter how long I wait,

392
00:32:00,520 --> 00:32:03,260
Hye Ri won't show up.

393
00:32:04,310 --> 00:32:09,470
So I looked for Eun Ho, and she was gone.

394
00:32:09,470 --> 00:32:12,310
That's why I came here.

395
00:32:13,210 --> 00:32:16,020
I thought maybe you knew…

396
00:32:16,020 --> 00:32:18,450
where Ju Eun Ho was.

397
00:32:18,450 --> 00:32:21,780
Where she is and what she's doing.

398
00:32:22,580 --> 00:32:24,940
Do you happen to know?

399
00:32:27,190 --> 00:32:30,500
I want to see Ju Eun Ho.

400
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:34,500
I want her to be Hye Ri, but if not,

401
00:32:36,630 --> 00:32:39,020
I'd like to at least see Eun Ho,

402
00:32:39,990 --> 00:32:43,010
and I have so much to tell her.

403
00:32:51,910 --> 00:32:55,300
Eun Ho took a leave of absence a month ago

404
00:32:55,300 --> 00:32:57,480
and hasn't been back since.

405
00:32:59,310 --> 00:33:02,470
I can't reach her, either.

406
00:33:06,760 --> 00:33:08,540
I see.

407
00:33:11,590 --> 00:33:13,330
Did Eun Ho…

408
00:33:14,390 --> 00:33:16,720
say she likes you?

409
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:23,480
As I've said, Sunbaenim,

410
00:33:24,390 --> 00:33:28,460
Eun Ho never told me that she likes me.

411
00:33:28,460 --> 00:33:30,630
Hye Ri, who is inside Eun Ho, and I

412
00:33:31,550 --> 00:33:35,450
shared feelings for each other.

413
00:33:37,490 --> 00:33:40,060
So did you break up?

414
00:33:42,140 --> 00:33:43,720
No.

415
00:33:45,750 --> 00:33:47,660
Hye Ri just disappeared.

416
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:49,820
If she comes back,

417
00:33:50,930 --> 00:33:53,310
will you date her again?

418
00:33:57,510 --> 00:33:59,150
Yes.

419
00:34:06,150 --> 00:34:08,870
Does that surprise you, Sunbaenim?

420
00:34:11,200 --> 00:34:12,770
No.

421
00:34:14,970 --> 00:34:17,580
I'm surprised by too many things.

422
00:34:17,580 --> 00:34:19,950
I can't sort out just one.

423
00:34:20,810 --> 00:34:22,520
But more than that…

424
00:34:23,160 --> 00:34:26,920
the fact you and Eun Ho were together, I—

425
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:31,120
Dissociative Identity Disorder is a disorder by its name,

426
00:34:31,120 --> 00:34:33,160
an illness.

427
00:34:34,780 --> 00:34:37,170
That means…

428
00:34:37,170 --> 00:34:40,620
Ju Eun Ho was very sick.

429
00:34:40,620 --> 00:34:43,570
The fact that she disappeared so suddenly

430
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:47,480
means she was in a lot of pain.

431
00:34:49,030 --> 00:34:50,930
Sunbaenim…

432
00:34:52,420 --> 00:34:55,090
don't you care about that at all?

433
00:34:56,510 --> 00:34:59,680
Don't you care Ju Eun Ho was in pain?

434
00:35:00,450 --> 00:35:04,450
Do you care only that she dated me in her condition?

435
00:35:06,060 --> 00:35:08,640
I'm asking because I'm curious.

436
00:35:08,640 --> 00:35:10,890
Sunbaenim,

437
00:35:12,580 --> 00:35:14,930
what's important to you?

438
00:35:38,970 --> 00:35:40,410
 Are you sick? 

439
00:35:40,410 --> 00:35:42,220
 Yes. I'm sick. 

440
00:35:42,220 --> 00:35:44,230
 Hyun Oh. 

441
00:35:44,230 --> 00:35:45,690
 Yes? Tell me. 

442
00:35:45,690 --> 00:35:48,900
 I already have a doctor whom I see. 

443
00:35:56,400 --> 00:36:01,970
   

444
00:36:03,640 --> 00:36:06,770
 Hello, Jung Hyun Oh? 

445
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:10,690
 Oh, yes. Hello. 

446
00:36:16,200 --> 00:36:20,760
 Doctor, I'm Ju Eun Ho's colleague. 

447
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:23,910
 Yes. How can I help you? 

448
00:36:24,770 --> 00:36:27,420
I mean, I actually…

449
00:36:28,240 --> 00:36:31,160
used to be Eun Ho's boyfriend.

450
00:36:31,160 --> 00:36:35,020
I heard that she has Dissociative Identity Disorder.

451
00:36:35,020 --> 00:36:40,110
Did you come in to hear about Ju Eun Ho?

452
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:44,420
Eun Ho is alone. She has no guardian so I—

453
00:36:44,420 --> 00:36:50,300
No, I'm sorry. We do not provide information about our patients.

454
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:54,580
I am obligated to keep patient discussions confidential.

455
00:36:54,580 --> 00:36:57,280
- Eun Ho— 
 - Hyun Oh.

456
00:36:57,280 --> 00:37:03,000
As I've said, I cannot help you with that.

457
00:37:10,940 --> 00:37:17,250
But if you don't mind, how about we talk about you?

458
00:37:36,410 --> 00:37:38,010
 I… 

459
00:37:38,660 --> 00:37:41,190
 Yes, tell me. 

460
00:37:44,430 --> 00:37:47,140
 I'm heartbroken. 

461
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:51,750
Do you mean your heart is in pain?

462
00:37:51,750 --> 00:37:54,620
Yes. My heart.

463
00:37:56,070 --> 00:38:00,250
Could you be more specific?

464
00:38:01,140 --> 00:38:03,010
So…

465
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:08,180
I had a girlfriend I broke up with four years ago.

466
00:38:08,180 --> 00:38:09,950
She…

467
00:38:12,660 --> 00:38:16,430
She has Dissociative Identity Disorder,

468
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:20,480
but I heard about it

469
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:26,600
from the man she dated as her other personality.

470
00:38:28,070 --> 00:38:29,710
I know,

471
00:38:30,610 --> 00:38:33,630
I have no right.

472
00:38:33,630 --> 00:38:35,740
But Doctor,

473
00:38:36,680 --> 00:38:39,830
honestly, I didn't want to break up with her.

474
00:38:39,830 --> 00:38:43,570
You mean, you didn't want to break up with your girlfriend?

475
00:38:43,570 --> 00:38:45,100
Correct.

476
00:38:45,100 --> 00:38:49,670
If I could, I would be with her forever,

477
00:38:49,670 --> 00:38:52,010
but I had to break up with her.

478
00:38:52,010 --> 00:38:56,950
I think then she developed Dissociative Identity Disorder.

479
00:38:58,010 --> 00:39:00,590
She lived as a different person,

480
00:39:01,300 --> 00:39:03,910
and I had no idea.

481
00:39:05,410 --> 00:39:10,280
How did you feel when you found out about it, Hyun Oh?

482
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:12,470
I was shocked.

483
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:17,000
But what was equally shocking was the fact…

484
00:39:17,570 --> 00:39:21,500
she was with another man as her other personality.

485
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:28,240
 I mean… 

486
00:39:28,240 --> 00:39:31,770
 how can I think only of myself in this situation? 

487
00:39:33,090 --> 00:39:36,880
 Do you think you're being selfish? 

488
00:39:37,850 --> 00:39:42,070
 I want to know why she is sick. 

489
00:39:42,700 --> 00:39:45,080
Is it because of me?

490
00:39:45,790 --> 00:39:48,800
Is it my fault that she has this illness?

491
00:39:48,800 --> 00:39:51,030
Because…

492
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:53,660
this feels as if I am to blame.

493
00:39:54,340 --> 00:39:59,470
I see. It sounds as if this is a very difficult time for you.

494
00:39:59,470 --> 00:40:02,080
Dissociative Identity Disorder

495
00:40:02,080 --> 00:40:07,210
may be widely known to involve past trauma or stress,

496
00:40:07,210 --> 00:40:10,580
but many other factors affect it.

497
00:40:10,580 --> 00:40:15,680
So we can't determine it was your fault.

498
00:40:16,930 --> 00:40:19,610
Did I cause her to struggle and suffer?

499
00:40:19,610 --> 00:40:24,330
Is that why she's sick? Is this all due to me?

500
00:40:24,890 --> 00:40:26,720
Hyun Oh.

501
00:40:26,720 --> 00:40:31,700
I understand you want to help Eun Ho,

502
00:40:31,700 --> 00:40:35,710
but what we discuss is related to Eun Ho.

503
00:40:35,710 --> 00:40:41,110
I have to talk to Eun Ho first and get her approval,

504
00:40:41,110 --> 00:40:45,850
that she wants your help before I can help you.

505
00:40:47,020 --> 00:40:51,820
But… she didn't tell me any of this.

506
00:40:54,660 --> 00:40:59,070
Hyun Oh, it seems you are worried

507
00:40:59,070 --> 00:41:04,670
that breaking up with her might have really hurt Eun Ho.

508
00:41:06,710 --> 00:41:09,780
Yes, I am.

509
00:41:12,020 --> 00:41:17,180
I worry it hurt her intensely.

510
00:41:18,240 --> 00:41:21,100
That she will never get better.

511
00:41:21,100 --> 00:41:22,800
Doctor.

512
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:26,840
How do you treat Dissociative Identity Disorder?

513
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:30,930
Does she need hospitalization? Should she take medication?

514
00:41:31,640 --> 00:41:33,830
If necessary,

515
00:41:33,830 --> 00:41:40,050
but the important thing is to talk it out and let wounds heal.

516
00:41:41,010 --> 00:41:45,200
If Eun Ho needs help during treatment,

517
00:41:45,200 --> 00:41:48,800
just knowing someone is by her side

518
00:41:48,800 --> 00:41:52,630
will be very assuring.

519
00:42:04,570 --> 00:42:06,700
 Eun Ho. 

520
00:42:06,700 --> 00:42:10,100
 Ju Eun Ho, are you inside? 

521
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,890
Ju Eun Ho!

522
00:42:17,570 --> 00:42:19,570
Eun Ho!

523
00:42:38,400 --> 00:42:44,890
   

524
00:42:45,770 --> 00:42:49,080
   

