00:43:01,410 --> 00:43:06,610
♪ Me? Me? Me? I'm the best ♪

526
00:43:06,610 --> 00:43:11,050
♪ I'm the best, best, best anchor. I am ♪

527
00:43:11,050 --> 00:43:13,830
♪ Let's go, go, go ♪

528
00:43:13,830 --> 00:43:17,470
Hyun Oh, I came to ask you a question.

529
00:43:17,470 --> 00:43:19,710
Do you know where Ju Eun Ho went on vacation?

530
00:43:19,710 --> 00:43:21,390
Is she living somewhere else for a month?

531
00:43:21,390 --> 00:43:24,870
I want to try that kind of thing, too.

532
00:43:25,460 --> 00:43:27,860
I don't know, either.

533
00:43:27,860 --> 00:43:29,340
I see.

534
00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:31,910
Did her sister go with her, too?

535
00:43:31,910 --> 00:43:36,370
